(15, 'about_us', '<p>Have you ever wondered who is behind the scenes of your favorite Nillgiri.com? What drives us to offer the best products and services? Get to know us better as we dive into who we are and what we do. From our mission to our values, we&#39;ll tell you all about our company and the people who make it happen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nillgiri was formed on 10 Dec 2022 by the initiative of three young and energetic people,&nbsp; Mr. Muhammad Mir Hossain in the role of CEO, Mr. Shaiful Islam Shawon as Director, and Mr. Mubin Al Hasan also as Director with the goal of making online shopping easier and more convenient for everyone involved. At our online mall customers can order and get their desired product/s&nbsp; delivered home upon payment. Our vendors will process customer orders in the shortest possible time to ship the goods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a multivendor eCommerce platform. We empower sellers by giving them a platform to sell their products and reach a bigger base of customers. We also provide buyers with a huge catalog to choose from, so they can find what they&#39;re looking for all in one place.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are proud to have helped numerous businesses grow and expand their reach, and we continue to work hard every day to make Nillgiri the best it can be. If you&#39;re looking for an easy and convenient way to buy or sell products online, this is the perfect platform for you. With our ever-growing catalog of products and users, you&#39;re sure to find what you&#39;re looking for on our site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are committed to providing the best possible experience for both buyers and sellers. Our platform is easy to use and provides sellers with all the tools they need to succeed. Our team is constantly working to improve our platform and provide outstanding customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our multivendor eCommerce is the perfect solution for anyone looking to start or grow their online business.</p>', NULL, '2022-12-05 11:44:27'),
