('App\\Model\\Product', 45, 'bd', 'name', 'POWER KNIGHT PRO FIBER HAIR MASK', 25),
('App\\Model\\Product', 45, 'bd', 'description', '<h2>POWER KNIGHT PRO FIBER HAIR MASK</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This super smoothing Detangeling hair treatment is one of our most effective hair treatments.</li>\r\n	<li>It is designed to successfully treat damaged hair and aid the recovery from any previous chemical treatments.</li>\r\n	<li>Our unique formula promotes healthy and strong hair, reducing split ends and breakage and giving instant results of revitalized, smooth and manageable hair.</li>\r\n	<li>Results may vary depending on the application and texture of hair.</li>\r\n</ul>', 26),
('App\\Model\\Product', 66, 'bd', 'name', 'Scru Cream For pink lips', 27),
('App\\Model\\Product', 66, 'bd', 'description', '<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Brand</td>\r\n			<td>Balai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Product benefits</td>\r\n			<td>Moisturizing,Exfoliating</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Active ingredients</td>\r\n			<td>Vitamin e,sodium hyaluronate</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h1>About this item</h1>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>★If your chapped lips are keeping you from showing your smile, our propolis lip scrub is here to change that.</li>\r\n	<li>★This scrub is a safe, gentle, and effective way to banish dry, flaky lips. Use it to exfoliate twice a week for a smile you&rsquo;ll have a hard time hiding.</li>\r\n	<li>★You don&#39;t need to apply lip balm every hour to keep your lips healthy. Our exfoliator works wonders to clear away dead skin and other junk while nourishing your lips with some of our favorite oils and extracts.</li>\r\n	<li>★When you&rsquo;re done, your lips will exude health, happiness, and radiance - and they will feel as healthy as they look.</li>\r\n	<li>★Package Contents:1 Pcs Professional Moisturizing Lip Cream Crystal Clear &amp; Hydrated Skin with Water Science Remove Dead Skin Exfoliating Lip Scrub Care</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h1><strong>Product description</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Balai Propolis Lip Exfoliating Gel Moisturizing Anti-Drying Firming Skin Lips Care Product</p>\r\n\r\n<h1><strong>Description:</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>1.This product has super moisturizing effect. The product is rich in sodium hyaluronate, which can deeply penetrate the skin and tightly lock the moisture of the skin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.This product has a good nourishing effect. The product is rich in collagen, which can provide enough collagen for the lips and deeply nourish the skin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.The product is rich in vitamin E collagen, which can promote the growth of lip muscles, remove the aging skin tissue, make the skin of the lips more full and more elastic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.The rose extract in the product has a good whitening nourishing function, which can make the lips more red and shiny.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.This product is lightweight and easy to carry, so you can moisturize your lips at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type:Lip care product</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gender:Unisex</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Color:Clear</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shelf life:3 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Feature:Moisturizing, Anti-Drying, Exfoliating</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NET WT:12g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Size:10*3*3cm/3.94*1.18*1.18&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package included:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x Propolis Lip Exfoliating Gel</p>', 28),
('App\\Model\\Product', 73, 'bd', 'name', 'Yogurt Milk Underarm Cream', 29),
('App\\Model\\Product', 73, 'bd', 'description', '<h2>Highlights</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>[Function] : 7 in 1 benefits - Reduce Odor, Smoothen Skin,</li>\r\n	<li>Non Irritate Skin, Natural Deodorant, Whiten Underarm, Reduce Dark Spots, Minimizes Pores.</li>\r\n	<li>After shower, towel dry and apply A Bonne Whitening Underarm Cream onto the underarm area.</li>\r\n	<li>[Main Ingredients] : Milk Protein, Aloe Vera, Vitamin B3, Glutathione, Wasabi, Willow Beak Extract.</li>\r\n	<li>[Registration No.] : 10-1-6009119, Product of Thailand.</li>\r\n	<li>[100% Satisfaction Guarantee] - 100% MONEY GUARANTEE.</li>\r\n	<li>7 in 1- fade melanin, wrinkles, remove the smell, anti-inflammatory, repair, whitening, replenishment</li>\r\n	<li>Enriched with multiple natural fruit extracts that help lighten dull armpits, firm,repair rough pores after hair removal</li>\r\n	<li>Moisturize and soothe the underarm skin, making it look fair, smooth, soft and bright</li>\r\n	<li>It also helps remove underarm odor and keeps the skin fresh and soothe</li>\r\n	<li>It has mild properties and causes no irritaion.</li>\r\n</ul>', 30),
('App\\Model\\Product', 96, 'bd', 'name', 'Aveeno Active Naturals Daily Moisturizing Lotion (200gm)', 31),
('App\\Model\\Product', 96, 'bd', 'description', '<p>The unique formula of Aveeno Daily Moisturising Lotion is clinically proven to go beyond 24 hour moisturisation and replenish the skin&rsquo;s natural barrier function, to significantly improve the condition of dry skin in just 2 weeks.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Absorbs quickly and leaves skin looking and feeling soft, smooth and healthy.</li>\r\n	<li>Fragrance and paraben free.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Significantly improves the condition of dry skin in just 2 weeks</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Moisturises skin for 24 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Available in two sizes: 200ml and 300ml</li>\r\n	<li>For best results, apply daily after your bath or shower.</li>\r\n</ul>', 32),
('App\\Model\\Product', 145, 'bd', 'name', 'WOW Red Onion Skin Mist Toner - 200 ml', 33),
('App\\Model\\Product', 145, 'bd', 'description', '<h2>Product details of WOW Red Onion Skin Mist Toner - 200 ml</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rejuvenate your tired, aging skin with WOW Skin Science Red Onion Black Seed Oil Skin Mist Toner. It is a hydrating, reviving and repairing facial mist to help you get dewy youthful skin. This spray offers you the dual benefit of toner and mist. It aids in minimizing pores and firming up skin and also delivers instant moisture to dehydrated skin.The formulation is loaded with skin-loving natural actives like skin repairing red onion seed extract and black seed oil. Witch hazel in the water helps to tone and soothe your skin. Aloe vera hydrates the skin and restores its natural moisture mantle.This facial mist toner can be used to wipe away excess sebum and residual dirt from your skin. It also hydrates dry, dehydrated skin and smoothens fine lines. The mist helps to calm and balance skin while refreshing dull, tired skin. It makes skin supple and reduces visible signs of aging. When you need an instant pick-me-up for dull, tired skin, reach for this mist toner. Simply spray it on your skin and see it revived.WHY YOU WOULD LOVE THIS MIST TONERHelps to repair and revive aging skin.Helps to hydrate skin and keep it soft.Helps to refresh and revive dull skin.Safe and skin friendly always.KEY INGREDIENTSPurified Water, Glycerin (Vegetable Derived), Propanediol, Witch Hazel Extract, Aloe Vera Extract, Red Onion Seed Extract, Black Seed Oil, Polysorbate 20, Phenoxyethanol, Benzyl Alcohol, Fragrance &amp; Sodium Gluconate.HOW TO USECleanse your face thoroughly. Hold the bottle a few inches away from your face and spray the mist on your skin. Let the mist settle on the skin. Then gently dab your face with your palm. Your skin becomes dewy soft, and fresh. You can use it over your makeup, and when your skin feels drawn and tight mid-day to rehydrate. Use this with a cotton pad to wipe away grime and excess oil.</li>\r\n</ul>', 34),
